it.eng.spagobi.meta.model.physical
Interface PhysicalColumn

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
PhysicalColumnImpl
public interface PhysicalColumn
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Physical Column'.

The following features are supported:

  • Comment
  • Data Type
  • Type Name
  • Size
  • Octect Length
  • Decimal Digits
  • Radix
  • Default Value
  • Nullable
  • Position
  • Table

See Also:
PhysicalModelPackage.getPhysicalColumn()
